  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.998,
    "endTime": 39.928,
    "text": "Okay, one way to say goodbye is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.598,
    "endTime": 41.568,
    "text": "\"See ya!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.638,
    "endTime": 43.418,
    "text": "Now, what is \"ya?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.418,
    "endTime": 45.888,
    "text": "\"Ya\" is simply \"you.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.888,
    "endTime": 48.577999999999996,
    "text": "In spoken English, many native speakers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.578,
    "endTime": 50.518,
    "text": "instead of saying \"you\" when they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.518,
    "endTime": 52.938,
    "text": "saying goodbye, will not say \"See you.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.938,
    "endTime": 55.308,
    "text": "You CAN say \"See you.\" but it's also"
  },
  {
