    "text": "possible to say \"See ya!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.454,
    "endTime": 59.954,
    "text": "Now, this is much more informal,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.954,
    "endTime": 63.544,
    "text": "among friends, coworkers, classmates,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.544,
    "endTime": 65.28399999999999,
    "text": "people you know well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.46,
    "endTime": 69.46,
    "text": "So \"See Ya!\" just means \"See you.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.407,
    "endTime": 74.407,
    "text": "We'll put that here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.495,
    "endTime": 78.495,
    "text": "Now, \"See you,\" you can follow this with"
  },
  {
